n the public domain.&#xA;More information on OSINT resources can be found through the OSINT Framework website &lt;a href=&#34;https://osintframework.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;https://osintframework.com/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
